Also i didnt know how many variables we were supposed to take into account, like in the balloon one: where did she stick the pin in the balloon? did she stick it in fast or slow? by popped do you mean the sudden bang or do you also count if it leaked out air slowly? etc

or spilling nail polish on the carpet. did he spill it and immediately try to clean it, or did he spill the nail polish on all the carpets before trying to clean it up? what kind of nail polish is it? what did he use to try and get the stain out?

maybe i&quotecharm thinking about it too hard
